title: Flight Simulator 2020- MSFS Update - new local legend + city update - now available
description:
In this video we will review local legend 16 as well as city update 7. The Short SC. 7 Skyvan is the 16th local legend which has been released and is a multi purpose aircraft which can be used for multiple scenarios: dropping parachutes for example. In addition to this European Cities II has been released as the city update. This package will update Nice, Monaco, Stockholm, Barcelona, Madrid and Porto.

0:00 intro
0:10 review: local legend 16: The Short SC.7 Skyvan
2:19 review: city update 7: European cities 2
5:04 install city update 7: multiple steps required
